divs: Sighting DetailsI was not aware that I had taken a photo of whatever this is until I started posting the photos on our vacation blog after I returned from California. The photo was taken from the 33rd floor of the Manchester Hyatt. It might be one of the planets that somehow was visable during the day. Also, this photo was shot through glass, however the white thing does not appear in any of the other photos I took within seconds of each other.
